{"id":672689,"date":[{"year":1984,"month":4,"day":15}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"88","ytitle":"","mtitle":"改革","ftitle":"——闻福建五十五位厂长要求“松绑”有感","authors":["叶尚志"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜借东风及劲吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今番度势莫徘徊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不堪积重真难返，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要驾轻也易追。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万马嘶鸣因待命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军踊跃欲争魁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗船箭橹俱齐备，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地利天时靠作为。"}]}